---
description: when testing UI in Shopware 6 Admin or Storefront
alwaysApply: false
---

- after adding product to cart, make sure to check that it was added before proceeding
- after a page transition, target a content element for visibility before proceeding to ensure the page is loaded
- I suggest waiting for page headings to load (inside vital components) when changing pages and tabs 
- Do not wait for network idle, the admin pages keep querying behind the scene infinitely
